Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.05,0:00:35.15,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}当我闭上双眼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.56,0:00:39.60,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}一切都是那么令我感到惊讶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.90,0:00:44.00,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}他们的身影又再度清楚浮现
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.65,0:00:48.80,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}活生生出现在我的银幕里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.15,0:00:53.61,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}我爱人的脸庞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.07,0:00:58.27,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}我战斗时的脸孔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.39,0:01:07.60,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}全部都在我的脑海里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.28,0:01:12.78,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}再给我们一天的时间 让我们找到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.90,0:01:17.06,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}引领到你世界的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.32,0:01:22.00,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}再给我一个晚上 让你能再看到我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.22,0:01:25.50,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}我就会相信这一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.70,0:01:29.53,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}回忆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.20,0:01:34.92,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,600)}{\be1}回忆啊
