Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.51,0:23:29.24,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}约定的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.80,0:23:33.74,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}我们注视着
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.00,0:23:38.47,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}我对运气
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.64,0:23:43.73,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}无所指望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.01,0:23:48.38,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}对这胸中的光荣的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.44,0:23:52.36,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}沉重的负担
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.55,0:23:55.90,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}有所准备
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.44,0:24:02.89,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}我将自行斩断退路
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.08,0:24:06.71,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}为实现野心
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.85,0:24:10.37,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}向前走
